          .mobile-shop-container {
            width: 96% !important;
            max-width: 350px !important;
            top: -50px !important;
          }
        }
      </style></div><div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center lg:mt-28 mb-12"><div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start"><img src="/car-images/infiniti-hero.jpg" alt="Used Infiniti auto parts hero image" class="w-full max-w-md rounded-2xl shadow-xl"/></div><div class="flex flex-col justify-center"><h3 class="font-semibold text-xl md:text-2xl mb-3 text-white">Used Infiniti Auto Parts for Sale</h3><p class="text-[18px] leading-[30px] text-[#cecece]">Smart. Affordable. Reliable. That’s PartsCentral. Infiniti drivers expect more refined power, premium design, and cutting-edge tech. At PartsCentral, we deliver quality-tested OEM Infiniti auto parts that match your vehicle’s standard — without the dealership markup. From high-performance sedans to luxe SUVs, we help keep your Infiniti performing at its best.</p></div></div><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-14"><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Smart. Affordable. Reliable. That’s PartsCentral.</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>Quality-tested OEM Infiniti auto parts</li><li>Nationwide shipping across the United States</li><li>Premium performance without dealership pricing</li><li>Designed to preserve Infiniti precision and luxury</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Designed for Precision. Driven by Passion.</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Owning an Infiniti isn’t about showing off. It’s about showing up with style and confidence. Whether you&#x27;re behind the wheel of a QX60, G37, or FX35, you know driving is more than movement — it’s a statement. We supply Infiniti owners who value form and function equally. Precision parts curated to perform.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Infiniti Parts We Offer</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>Engines, transmissions, cooling systems</li><li>Radiators, AC compressors, fans</li><li>Starters, alternators, battery modules</li><li>Doors, mirrors, fenders, grilles</li><li>Window motors and regulators</li><li>Axles, control arms, suspension parts</li><li>Lighting, interior switches, sensors</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Real Infiniti Parts. Tested and Trusted</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Each part undergoes careful inspection by our expert team to ensure safety, durability, and smooth integration with your vehicle. Because every Infiniti deserves parts that keep it sharp and road-ready.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Save More. Compromise Less</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">OEM Infiniti parts don’t have to break your budget. Submit a quick quote request online — no login required. We’ll respond within minutes with your best price. Searching for Infiniti auto parts near me or a trusted Infiniti junkyard near me? PartsCentral brings it all to your screen.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Infiniti Models We Support</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">We supply parts for nearly every Infiniti model. Rare model or discontinued production? We can source it.</p><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1 text-[#cecece]"><li>Infiniti EX35</li><li>Infiniti FX35</li><li>Infiniti FX45</li><li>Infiniti FX50</li><li>Infiniti G20</li><li>Infiniti G25</li><li>Infiniti G35</li><li>Infiniti G37</li><li>Infiniti I30</li><li>Infiniti I35</li><li>Infiniti J30</li><li>Infiniti M35</li><li>Infiniti M37</li><li>Infiniti M45</li><li>Infiniti Q30</li><li>Infiniti Q40</li><li>Infiniti Q45</li><li>Infiniti Q50</li><li>Infiniti Q60</li><li>Infiniti Q70</li><li>Infiniti QX30</li><li>Infiniti QX50</li><li>Infiniti QX56</li><li>Infiniti QX60</li><li>Infiniti QX70</li><li>Infiniti QX80</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Why Infiniti Owners Choose PartsCentral</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>Rigorous quality inspections</li><li>Nationwide shipping</li><li>Competitive pricing</li><li>Secure checkout and easy returns</li><li>Prompt customer support available 7 days a week</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Get the Infiniti Feel Back</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">From Q series sedans to full-size QX SUVs, we help you get the specific Infiniti auto parts that restore performance, luxury, and reliability. Search by model and request a quote today. Infiniti owners across the country already trust PartsCentral.</p><p class="mt-4 font-bold text-white">Request a free quote today.</p></div></div><div class="w-full mt-20 py-16 sm:py-20 px-4 sm:px-8  bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 text-center rounded-2xl"><h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Find Quality <!-- -->Used Infiniti Auto Parts for Sale<!-- --> Parts Today?</h2><p class="text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 text-sm sm:text-base">Get fast pricing, expert guidance, and nationwide delivery on quality used auto parts for your <!-- -->Used Infiniti Auto Parts for Sale<!-- -->.</p><a href="/" class="inline-block  bg-[#00A3FF]  text-white px-7 sm:px-9 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,163,255,0.45)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(0,163,255,0.7)] transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-95">Find My Parts</a></div></section><section class="w-full flex flex-col items-center px-6 py-16 bg-[#07142B] text-[#E8F3FF]"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-orbitron mb-10 text-center">USED <!-- -->INFINITI<!-- --> AUTO PARTS</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto"><ul class="space-y-2 text-lg leading-7 font-jaldi list-disc list-insid